{"tid":1333470,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"有冇人識解車公簽","createTime":"2019-07-19T16:51:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T14:30:37.000Z","uid":95571,"like":38,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"a7bd4f937a34a494c4e25b56dc40efdf5b8c7ea5","tid":1333470,"uid":95571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:51:54.000Z","msg":"幫香港示威者721求左簽<br />\n車公靈簽 第五十簽：上簽 <br />\n簽文：困甚離家歲月長，失群孤雁正思量；馬牛不及終須及，縱事無方卻有方<br />\n解簽：先難後易，家宅安吉，自身平安，求財大吉 <br />\n斷簽：家宅貧困，佔病拖延，自身忍耐，出入不吉，婚姻不合，離異，求財莫問，離鄉別井，欲歸不得，畜牲不如，後有轉機 <br />\n家宅：平安大吉 <br />\n出行：在途中 <br />\n姻緣：不宜急進 <br />\n行人：未動身 <br />\n生育：註意調理 <br />\n訴訟：可有和解之機 <br />\n事業：成功在望 <br />\n搬遷：遠居不宜 <br />\n自身：需多思考 <br />\n疾病：可痊愈 <br />\n財運：先苦後甜"},{"pid":"d4c8446c15931d10e89a9f005432ec67c509e82c","tid":1333470,"uid":95571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:52:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d21bc21e0a08e241176ae8f5528f0ef147d37a3","tid":1333470,"uid":95571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:52:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f43c6d8745e9377b41391686edf267fcf1cea4e","tid":1333470,"uid":95571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:52:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"583dea5c884f9de4fc455a66bb0851a31bac835f","tid":1333470,"uid":95571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:55:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe388fd3e15272d18fe59af35658816ce404e7e7","tid":1333470,"uid":95571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,